{"tid":1322950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"期待手持午餐肉就有閪屌的日子","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:57:19.000Z","uid":57073,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88046cd369b3905cb3e4350501d4aa4ab6e653b7","tid":1322950,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2047</span>又好,927又好,UFO又好,<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戒嚴又好</span></span>,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924276.jpg&h=0447ef5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924275.jpg&h=8ac8e8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924274.jpg&h=4662e826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baeca7d85af92c16dfb450ba360ceb0dce78550f","tid":1322950,"uid":144508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76d189f12e6e4e7c098eeb694e973d24fc087a0","tid":1322950,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"有無啲就過期？<br />\n唔好浪費 攞出去喂狗"},{"pid":"c161a3ae2b11f3979a76f850b885b393c32977d6","tid":1322950,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6409cfdcd7ac79c0a1a825a8b5c3968a29115058","tid":1322950,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"夢想成真了"},{"pid":"1fdbd53815953626b93ab3cd43fa537aea4b96bc","tid":1322950,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b76d189f12e6e4e7c098eeb694e973d24fc087a0","tid":1322950,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"有無啲就過期？<br />\n唔好浪費 攞出去喂狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"d 狗唔晒午餐肉都有得喺差館屌女神啦"},{"pid":"8b4990fcd021da8a3fea59bf1d39de58437883e1","tid":1322950,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a83093b910614ac5c2f9d77c3834c0be7771e0","tid":1322950,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"埋圖2012年loop 到宜家，d罐頭過晒期未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3fecf04eb9f6530a5fb1ed7ad5cfdac60b15d2","tid":1322950,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下